import React from "react" import { FaArrowAltCircleRight, FaArrowAltCircleLeft} from 'react-icons/fa' function Home() { return(

Welcome to Gathered Magic where you can create the Magic: The Gathering Deck of your dreams!

Directions

  • From the search page, type in the name of the card you are looking for, either partial or full
  • Select from the list the card you wish to add by clicking "Add to decklist"
  • Keep tabs on your decklist from the decklist page
) } export default Home;
